│        "topic_title": "Deploying a simple containerized application",             │
│        "theory_explanation": "This is where all the concepts we've discussed so   │
│  far come together! Deploying a simple containerized application means taking     │
│  your well-packed Docker container, telling ECS/Fargate how to run it (using a    │
│  Task Definition), and then setting up an ECS Service to keep it running          │
│  reliably. It's like the grand finale of our container journey!\n\nHere's a       │
│  simplified breakdown of the steps you'd typically follow:\n\n1.  **Create your   │
