│  often *why* it happened. You can use them to troubleshoot issues, understand     │
│  user behavior, and ensure your application is running as expected.\n\nThe        │
│  documentation provides a guide to getting started with collecting and storing    │
│  these vital records, and the video offers a comprehensive tutorial.",            │
