│  line doesn't get too long (throttling), and makes sure everything is             │
│  secure.\n\nAmazon API Gateway is a fully managed service that acts as the        │
│  \"front door\" for your applications. It allows you to create, publish,          │
│  maintain, monitor, and secure REST (Representational State Transfer) APIs at     │
│  any scale. For serverless applications, it's crucial because it enables          │
