│        "topic_title": "Managing EC2 instances with Boto3",                        │
│        "theory_explanation": "Amazon EC2 (Elastic Compute Cloud) provides         │
│  virtual computers, or **instances**, that you can rent and run in the cloud.     │
│  Think of them as powerful, customizable servers that you can spin up, use, and   │
