│  needs. Periodically check your IAM policies to ensure they still adhere to the   │
│  principle of least privilege. Remove any unnecessary permissions.\n6.            │
│  **Encrypt Your Data:** Protect sensitive information by encrypting it, both      │
│  when it's stored (at rest) and when it's moving between services (in transit).   │
│  Services like KMS (which we'll cover next) make this much easier.\nThe video     │
